10bbc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERene%20Byrd%20got%20pregnant%20at%20age%2048%20thanks%20to%20IVF.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Rene%20Byrd%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20my%20pregnancy%2C%20I%20remember%20being%20scared%20of%20what%20this%20new%20life%20as%20a%20mother%20would%20look%20like.%20I%20had%20little%20panic%20attacks%20considering%20how%20different%20life%20would%20be%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20decades%20of%20life%20without%20a%20child.%20And%20then%20I%20felt%20guilty%2C%20telling%20myself%20I%20had%20waited%20so%20long%20for%20this.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20grappling%20with%20these%20thoughts%20until%20I%20realized%20my%20child%20would%20just%20be%20an%20extension%20of%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20our%20little%20boy%2C%20Crue%2C%20was%20born%20in%20November%202024%2C%20I%20felt%20ready%20for%20his%20arrival%20in%20theory.%20Having%20spent%20years%20hearing%20from%20friends%20with%20children%2C%20I%20had%20an%20idea%20of%20what%20to%20expect.%20Even%20still%2C%20those%20early%20days%20were%20a%20lot%20to%20deal%20with.%20All%20these%20things%20were%20being%20thrown%20at%20me%20about%20what%20I%20should%20and%20shouldn't%20do%20with%20a%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201400766-22c8-4251-92ec-24352faf1683%5C%22%3EBeing%20a%20mom%20in%20my%20late%2040s%20has%20so%20many%20beautiful%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20online%20mother%20and%20baby%20communities%20and%20in-person%20baby%20groups%2C%20finding%20my%20tribe%20of%20mothers%20like%20me%2C%20ones%20that%20were%20%26quot%3Bolder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20stillness%20within%20me%20that%20grounds%20me%20as%20I%20take%20care%20of%20Crue.%20I%20have%20this%20playbook%20of%20mothering%2C%20developed%20from%20years%20of%20research%20and%20observation%2C%20that%20has%20given%20me%20assurance%20that%20even%20when%20things%20don't%20seem%20to%20be%20going%20to%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20like%20breastfeeding%20or%20sleeping%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20OK%2C%20and%20so%20was%20he.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20built%20up%20financial%20security%2C%20I%20didn't%20worry%20about%20how%20I%20was%20going%20to%20provide%20for%20a%20baby.%20Established%20in%20a%20career%2C%20I%20could%20plan%20for%20all%20baby-related%20expenses%2C%20including%20IVF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20I%20had%20gotten%20so%20much%20out%20of%20my%20system%20in%20my%20younger%20years%20%E2%80%94%20corporate%20working%2C%20parties%2C%20nice%20restaurants%20%E2%80%94%20I%20felt%20content%20to%20settle%20in%20at%20home%20with%20my%20baby%20and%20husband.%20I%20never%20feel%20like%20I'm%20missing%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20concern%20I've%20heard%20quietly%20whispered%20in%20different%20circles%20is%20that%20of%20my%20health.%20I%20know%20that%20as%20I%20get%20older%2C%20little%20issues%20with%20my%20body%20could%20pop%20up%20%E2%80%94%20issues%20that%20I%20might%20not%20have%20had%20as%20a%20younger%20mother.%20This%20has%20forced%20me%20to%20look%20after%20my%20body%20more%20than%20I%20ever%20have%20so%20that%20I%20can%20fully%20enjoy%20time%20with%20Crue%20as%20he%20gets%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecoming%20a%20mother%20had%20always%20been%20a%20dream%20of%20mine.%20I%20trusted%20the%20process%2C%20holding%20on%20to%20hope%2C%20and%20although%20delayed%2C%20my%20dream%20finally%20came%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbecame-mom-fortyeight-ivf-corporate-world-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749936181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841c9d09b2a601d01b26361%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbecame-mom-fortyeight-ivf-corporate-world-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rene%20Byrd%20had%20frozen%20her%20eggs%20before%20she%20met%20her%20now-husband%20who%20is%20seven%20years%20younger%20than%20her.%20She%