ill%20talk%2C%20and%20more%20profound%20questions%20that%2C%20as%20a%20parent%2C%20moved%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20aren't%20hardcore%20fans%20like%20we%20are%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wild%20Robot%26quot%3B%20follows%20Rozzum%20Unit%207134%20(a.k.a%20Roz)%2C%20a%20machine%20that%20washes%20ashore%20on%20a%20remote%20island%20and%20must%20learn%20to%20survive%20%E2%80%94%20and%20eventually%2C%20thrive%20%E2%80%94%20among%20wildlife.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20extreme%20fish%20out%20of%20water%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20take%20that%20advanced%20technological%20character%20and%20you%20put%20it%20in%20the%20least%20technological%20place%20you%20can%20imagine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20book's%20premise%20is%20simple%2C%20but%20the%20emotional%20arc%20is%20complex.%20Brown%20imagined%20a%20robot%20that%20becomes%20more%20%26quot%3Bnatural%20and%20wild%20than%20even%20a%20person%20could.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20cried%20at%20different%20scenes%20of%20the%20movie%20because%20Roz%20reminded%20us%20of%20different%20parenting%20phases%20we've%20been%20through%2C%20helping%20our%20kids%20learn%20how%20to%20walk%2C%20or%20learning%20ourselves%20how%20to%20let%20them%20go%20and%20become%20their%20own%20person.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20kind%20of%20the%20main%20goal%20of%20an%20author%20%E2%80%94%20to%20make%20sure%20your%20readers%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2280991bed-f8f2-4835-9486-ec33e3db14aa%5C%22%3ERoz%20is%20an%20optimistic%20vision%20of%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20most%20portrayals%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-anthropic-dario-amodei-ai-jobs-vivatech-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20tend%20toward%20the%20dystopian%2C%20Brown%20aimed%20for%20something%20different.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20familiar%20with%20stories%20about%20robots%2C%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthese-are-12-of-the-greatest-movie-robots-of-all-time-2015-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobot%20uprising%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20it%20was%20more%20interesting%20to%20show%20a%20more%20optimistic%20vision%20of%20what%20the%20future%20could%20look%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20backs%20that%20vision%20with%20research%2C%20not%20just%20imagination.%20Brown%20visited%20NASA's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-science-high-demand-ai-what-to-know-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20spoke%20with%20scientists%20designing%20robots%20to%20explore%20other%20planets.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20already%20using%20robots%20to%20communicate%20with%20animals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20my%20son%2C%20who%20listened%20with%20both%20his%20eyes%20and%20mouth%20wide%20open%20in%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoz%2C%20Brown%20believes%2C%20could%20someday%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22813c9a1e-ae75-4617-846c-bdaa4d67d7a6%5C%22%3EThere%20might%20be%20a%20movie%20sequel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20has%20long%20loved%20animation%2C%20and%20the%20adaptation%20of%20the%20first%20book%20from%20his%20three-book%20series%20into%20a%20movie%C2%A0has%20been%20a%20surreal%20experience.%20%26quot%3BBefore%20I%20started%20writing%20children's%20books%2C%20I%20actually%20worked%20in%20animation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0So%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdreamworks-cofounder-ai-is-amazing-resource-for-hollywood-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDreamWorks%3C%2Fa%3E%20reached%20out%2C%20saying%20they%20wanted%20to%20adapt%20the%20book%20into%20a%20movie%2C%20he%20was%20very%20excited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20hopes%20for%20a%20sequel%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20the%20more%20important%20questions%20my%20son%20had%20because%20he%20wants%20more%20of%20Roz.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20pretty%20confident%20there%20will%20be%20at%20least%20one%20more%20movie%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20shared%20with%20Brown%20how%20his%20twin%20sisters%2C%20who%20are%20two%20years%20younger%20than%20him%2C%20often%20get%20distracted%20when%20my%20husband%20reads%20the%20original%20book%20because%20it%20doesn't%20have%20illustrations%20on%20every%20page.%20Brown's%20latest%20project%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D1da9e28ff6a3b4eb1edfcb65a74d128e61fad8bcbf8aee4eea11c022a5c5800f%26postID%3D684af91214270c4174af2718%26postSlug%3Dpeter-brown-wild-robot-interview-sequel-new-book-2025-6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FWild-Robot-Island-Peter-Brown%252Fdp%252F0316669466%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wild%20Robot%20on%20the%20Island%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20picture%20book%20adaptation%20of%20the%20original%20novel%2C%20aimed%20at%20an%20audience%20like%20my%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a617f99a-8159-4da5-8cb5-e3ae03069848%5C%22%3EHe%20wants%20readers%20to%20learn%20something%20from%20Roz%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20interview%2C%20Brown%20answered%20my%20son's%20big%20questions%20and%20little%20questions%20with%20the%20same%20enthusiasm%20and%20attention%20to%20detail.%20They%20talked%20about%20whether%20Brown%20had%20a%20Roomba%20(he%20doesn't)%20and%20whether%20he%20had%20adopted%20anything%20like%20Roz%20did%20in%20the%20story%20(he%20did%20adopt%20his%20dog%20Pam).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20surprised%20me%20by%20asking%20one%20of%20the%20more%20profound%20questions%20of%20the%20interview%20%E2%80%94%20what%20we%2C%20as%20readers%2C%20could%20learn%20from%20Roz.%20Brown%20hopes%20it's%20empathy%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falways-been-independent-accepting-help-support-makes-me-better-parent-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einterdependence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BRoz%20learns%20that%20she%20needs%20help.%20She%20can't%20do%20it%20all%20by%20herself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20all%20need%20each%20other%3B%20we%20should%20just%20be%20good%20to%20each%20other%20because%20we're%20going%20to%20need%20each%20other%20at%20some%20point%20or%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20message%20that%20Brown%20feels%20is%20often%20forgotten.%20But%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20a%20robot%20(or%20in%20my%20case%2C%20during%20this%20interview%2C%20a%207-year-old)%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20world%2C%20it%20becomes%20fresh%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-brown-wild-robot-interview-sequel-new-book-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749917461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684af9e285e81483682bf879%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-brown-wild-robot-interview-sequel-new-book-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%207-year-old%20son%20and%20I%20interviewed%20Peter%20Brown%20together.%20As%20big%20fans%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wild%20Robot%2C%26quot%3B%20we%20both%20had%20very%20different%20questions%20to%20ask.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpreti%40insider.com%20(Conz%20Preti)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-brown-wild-robot-interview-sequel-new-book-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US-Iran%20nuclear%20talks%20in%20Oman%20cancelled%20after%20Israel's%20strikes%20on%20Tehran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749917385000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-iran-nuclear-talks-in-oman-cancelled-after-israel-s-strikes-on-tehran-125061400804_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Iran%20US%20talks%20sc