hout%20any%20water%2C%20high%20heat%2C%20or%20segregating%20headaches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Boards%20that%20behave%20better%20than%20wood%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20output%3F%20Strong%2C%20durable%20boards%20that%20look%20like%20wood%20but%20are%20tougher%20%E2%80%94%20resistant%20to%20moisture%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20wear.%20All%20made%20without%20harming%20a%20single%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Big%20impact%2C%20small%20footprint%3A%2044%2C000%20chips%20packets%20save%20a%20mature%20tree%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20kilo%20of%20unWOOD%20reuses%20500g%20of%20waste%20plastic%20and%20cuts%20down%20one%20and%20a%20half%20kilogram%20of%20carbon%20emissions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EunWOOD%E2%80%99s%20outdoor%20benches%2C%20tables%2C%20railings%20and%20fencing%20have%20found%20a%20unique%20niche.%20%E2%80%9CSteel%20rusts%2C%20cement%20cracks%2C%20wood%20swells%20in%20moisture%2C%20and%20plastic%20breaks%20under%20the%20sun%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishal%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20solving%20all%20of%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%2011%20park%20benches%20made%20from%20unWOOD%20save%20one%20fully%20mature%20tree%2C%20and%20repurpose%20about%2014%2C000%20plastic%20bottles%2C%2044%2C000%20snack%20packets%2C%20or%201%2C500%20broken%20toys%20that%20would%20have%20otherwise%20polluted%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20officially%20launching%20as%20a%20company%20in%20April%202025%2C%20unWOOD%20has%20already%20recycled%20over%2010%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%20and%20saved%2031%20trees.%20And%20they%E2%80%99re%20just%20getting%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20learning%20meets%20sustainability%3A%20%E2%80%98Benches%20for%20Change%E2%80%99%20initiative%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20children%20in%20underserved%20Indian%20schools%20study%20seated%20on%20bare%20floors%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reality%20that%20affects%